### TESTES DE EMAIL - RESEND
### Configure a variável RESEND_API_KEY no .env antes de testar
### Servidor deve estar rodando em http://localhost:3000

### 1. Teste de Email de Boas-vindas
POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-welcome
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "name": "Bernardo"
}

###

### 2. Teste de Email de Verificação
POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "token": "teste-token-verificacao-12345"
}

###

### 3. Teste de Email de Reset de Senha
POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "token": "reset-token-12345"
}

###

### 4. Teste de Notificação de Aula Agendada
POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-lesson
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "lessonDetails": {
    "studentName": "João Silva",
    "instructorName": "Maria Santos",
    "date": "30/01/2026",
    "time": "14:00",
    "duration": 60
  }
}

###

### 5. Envio de Email Genérico (Requer Autenticação)
### Primeiro faça login e copie o token
POST http://localhost:3000/email/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_JWT_AQUI

{
  "to": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "subject": "Email de Teste",
  "html": "<h1>Olá!</h1><p>Este é um email de teste do SeuInstrutor.</p>"
}

###

### 6. Teste com Múltiplos Destinatários
POST http://localhost:3000/email/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_JWT_AQUI

{
  "to": ["email1@example.com", "email2@example.com"],
  "subject": "Email para Múltiplos Destinatários",
  "html": "<p>Este email foi enviado para várias pessoas.</p>"
}

###

### 7. Teste com CC e BCC
POST http://localhost:3000/email/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_JWT_AQUI

{
  "to": "berproenccaa@gmail.com",
  "cc": "copia@example.com",
  "bcc": "copia-oculta@example.com",
  "subject": "Email com CC e BCC",
  "html": "<p>Este email tem cópias.</p>"
}

###

### COMANDOS CURL (alternativa ao arquivo .http)

### Email de Boas-vindas
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-welcome \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"berproenccaa@gmail.com","name":"Bernardo"}'

### Email de Verificação
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-verification \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"berproenccaa@gmail.com","token":"teste-token-123"}'

### Email de Reset
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/email/test-reset-password \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"email":"berproenccaa@gmail.com","token":"reset-token-123"}'

